# .python-version
# BLUEPRINT: Composer 2 implements from this structure
# PURPOSE: Pin the Python version for pyenv, asdf, and mise version managers.
#          When a developer runs `pyenv install` or `mise install` in this directory,
#          the version specified here is installed and activated automatically.
#          Per spec §26.12 item 361.
# DESIGN DECISIONS:
#   - Value: 3.12 (minimum) or 3.12.x (pinned patch) — filled with specific version at initialization
#   - Use patch-level pin (e.g., 3.12.7) for maximum reproducibility
#   - Aligns with Python requirement in pyproject.toml [project] requires-python
#   - Updated when Python version is upgraded (with corresponding pyproject.toml update)
3.12
